                                                                                              SC-34(01)       NON-MODIFIABLE EXECUTABLE PROGRAMS | NO WRITABLE STORAGE
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              SC-34(01)_ODP         system components to be employed with no writeable storage are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SC-34(01)             <SC-34(01)_ODP system components> are employed with no writeable storage
                                                                                                                                    that is persistent across component restart or power on/oﬀ.

